{%- comment -%}
  Currency-B — switcher de divisa público para LedsC4 multi-currency.

  3 opciones expuestas al usuario: EUR (€), USD ($), GBP (£). El usuario
  no ve "Market" — sólo divisa.

  Mecanismo nativo Shopify: {% form 'localization' %} con
  <input name="currency_code"> + <input name="return_to">. Submit hace
  POST a /localization que cambia SOLO la presentment currency dentro
  del Market activo (NO toca country_code, así no dispara el guard B2B
  "You can't purchase for this location" cuando el cliente tiene una
  Company Location ligada a un Market concreto).

  Requisito Admin: el/los Market(s) activos deben tener EUR, USD y GBP
  habilitadas como divisas adicionales (Markets → … → Currency and
  pricing). En su defecto el POST devuelve la misma divisa y el flag de
  sessionStorage corta el bucle.

  Persistencia: cookie `ledsc4_currency` (30 días) recuerda la elección
  para reaplicarla si Shopify pierde el contexto de presentment.

  Persistencia + redirect 1-vez:
    - Al cargar, JS lee ledsc4_currency. Si no existe → setea 'EUR'.
    - Si la divisa de la cookie != localization.country.currency.iso_code
      activa → submit silencioso del form con country_code mapeado para
      forzar el Market correcto. Anti-bucle vía sessionStorage flag con
      la divisa intentada — si tras el redirect Shopify no aplicó el
      Market (e.g. country no soportado), el flag impide reintentar la
      misma divisa en esta sesión.
    - Al click en una opción: setea la cookie + limpia el flag de
      sessionStorage + submit del form. Esa elección manual sustituye
      cualquier estado previo.

  Sin auto-detect por IP (decisión Dani): por defecto EUR. Si la cookie
  vence o el navegador la borra, el usuario vuelve a aterrizar en EUR.

  Aria/HTML:
    Botón dropdown con aria-expanded, panel <ul> oculto por defecto.
    JS minimal autocontenido (no depende del JS del header).
    Outside-click + Escape cierran el panel.

  Render:
    Llamado desde b2b-header.liquid y b2b-header-simple.liquid junto al
    selector de idioma. Visible para todos los visitantes (no gated).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  # Divisa de presentment activa (la que se muestra y se cobra). En
  # Markets con varias divisas habilitadas, cart.currency.iso_code
  # refleja la selección actual del usuario; si no, cae a la base del
  # Market. Defensive default a 'EUR' para que JS no compare contra nil
  # y entre en bucle de redirect.
  assign active_currency = cart.currency.iso_code | default: 'EUR'
  assign active_symbol = '€'
  if active_currency == 'USD'
    assign active_symbol = '$'
  elsif active_currency == 'GBP'
    assign active_symbol = '£'
  endif

  # return_to: URL ABSOLUTA al primary domain (shop.url).
  #
  # Por qué absoluta y no relativa: Shopify hace 307 server-side del POST
  # /localization desde el custom domain (shop.ledsc4.com) al canonical
  # .myshopify.com para clientes B2B autenticados. Si el return_to es
  # relativo, tras el bounce el cliente resuelve contra .myshopify.com y
  # acaba allí sin sesión. Con return_to absoluto a shop.url, Shopify
  # respeta el host destino y el cliente vuelve al primary domain donde
  # sí tiene cookies de sesión válidas.
  assign return_path = shop.url | append: request.path
  if request.query_string != blank
    assign return_path = return_path | append: '?' | append: request.query_string
  endif
-%}

<div class="ledsc4-currency-switcher" data-ledsc4-currency-switcher>
  {%- form 'localization', class: 'ledsc4-currency-switcher__form' -%}
    <input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="{{ active_currency }}" data-ledsc4-currency-input>
    <input type="hidden" name="return_to" value="{{ return_path | escape }}">

    <button
      type="button"
      class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__toggle"
      aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controls="ledsc4-currency-panel"
      aria-label="{{ 'ledsc4.common.currency.switcher_label' | t }}"
      data-ledsc4-currency-toggle
    >
      <span aria-hidden="true">{{ active_symbol }}</span>
      <span>{{ active_currency }}</span>
      <span class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__caret" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
    </button>

    <ul
      id="ledsc4-currency-panel"
      class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel"
      role="list"
      data-ledsc4-currency-panel
    >
      <li>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__option{% if active_currency == 'EUR' %} ledsc4-currency-switcher__option--active{% endif %}"
          data-ledsc4-currency="EUR"
          {% if active_currency == 'EUR' %}aria-current="true"{% endif %}
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">€</span> EUR
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__option{% if active_currency == 'USD' %} ledsc4-currency-switcher__option--active{% endif %}"
          data-ledsc4-currency="USD"
          {% if active_currency == 'USD' %}aria-current="true"{% endif %}
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">$</span> USD
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="ledsc4-currency-switcher__option{% if active_currency == 'GBP' %} ledsc4-currency-switcher__option--active{% endif %}"
          data-ledsc4-currency="GBP"
          {% if active_currency == 'GBP' %}aria-current="true"{% endif %}
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">£</span> GBP
        </button>
      </li>
    </ul>
  {%- endform -%}
</div>

<style>
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher {
    position: relative;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__form { margin: 0; }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__toggle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground, 15 18 23));
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.15);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__toggle:hover {
    border-color: rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.3);
    background: rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.04);
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__caret {
    font-size: 0.7em;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__toggle[aria-expanded="true"] .ledsc4-currency-switcher__caret {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 0.25rem);
    right: 0;
    min-width: 140px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.08);
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.10);
    z-index: 60;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel.ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel--open {
    display: block;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__option {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground, 15 18 23));
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__option:hover {
    background: rgba(15, 18, 23, 0.06);
  }
  .ledsc4-currency-switcher__option--active {
    color: var(--color-ledsc4-accent, #1a1f27);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function () {
    var COOKIE_NAME = 'ledsc4_currency';
    var COOKIE_MAX_AGE = 60 * 60 * 24 * 30; // 30 días
    var SUPPORTED = { EUR: 1, USD: 1, GBP: 1 };
    var ACTIVE_CURRENCY = {{ active_currency | json }};
    var FLAG_KEY = 'ledsc4_currency_redirected';

    function getCookie(name) {
      var m = document.cookie.match(new RegExp('(?:^|; )' + name + '=([^;]*)'));
      return m ? decodeURIComponent(m[1]) : null;
    }
    function setCookie(name, value) {
      var secure = location.protocol === 'https:' ? '; Secure' : '';
      document.cookie =
        name + '=' + encodeURIComponent(value) +
        '; Path=/; Max-Age=' + COOKIE_MAX_AGE +
        '; SameSite=Lax' + secure;
    }

    var switcher = document.querySelector('[data-ledsc4-currency-switcher]');
    if (!switcher) return;
    var form = switcher.querySelector('form');
    var currencyInput = switcher.querySelector('[data-ledsc4-currency-input]');
    var toggle = switcher.querySelector('[data-ledsc4-currency-toggle]');
    var panel = switcher.querySelector('[data-ledsc4-currency-panel]');

    // --- Persistencia 30 días + redirect 1-vez si la cookie diverge ---
    var desired = getCookie(COOKIE_NAME);
    if (!desired || !SUPPORTED[desired]) {
      desired = 'EUR';
      setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, desired);
    }
    if (desired !== ACTIVE_CURRENCY) {
      // Anti-bucle: si ya intentamos esta divisa en esta sesión y el
      // Market no la admite como presentment, ACTIVE_CURRENCY no habrá
      // cambiado tras el redirect → no reintentar.
      var lastRedirect;
      try { lastRedirect = sessionStorage.getItem(FLAG_KEY); } catch (e) { lastRedirect = null; }
      if (lastRedirect !== desired && form && currencyInput) {
        try { sessionStorage.setItem(FLAG_KEY, desired); } catch (e) {}
        currencyInput.value = desired;
        form.submit();
        return;
      }
    } else {
      try { sessionStorage.removeItem(FLAG_KEY); } catch (e) {}
    }

    // --- Click en opción → set cookie + submit form ---
    switcher.querySelectorAll('[data-ledsc4-currency]').forEach(function (btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var cur = btn.getAttribute('data-ledsc4-currency');
        if (!cur || !SUPPORTED[cur] || !form || !currencyInput) return;
        setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, cur);
        try { sessionStorage.removeItem(FLAG_KEY); } catch (e2) {}
        currencyInput.value = cur;
        form.submit();
      });
    });

    // --- Dropdown open/close ---
    function closePanel() {
      if (!toggle || !panel) return;
      toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      panel.classList.remove('ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel--open');
    }
    if (toggle && panel) {
      toggle.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        e.stopPropagation();
        var expanded = toggle.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
        toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!expanded));
        panel.classList.toggle('ledsc4-currency-switcher__panel--open', !expanded);
      });
      document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        if (switcher.contains(e.target)) return;
        closePanel();
      });
      document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
        if (e.key === 'Escape') closePanel();
      });
    }
  })();
</script>
